snippet.description:

snippet.title: Identical Twins Switch Places | Will Bailey’s Boyfriend Notice? (Part 1)
snippet.description:
In today’s video, you’ll watch us #SWITCHPLACES and try to trick our friends, including Bailey’s boyfriend, Asa! Do you think they will fall for it??

✅ If you loved this video, don't forget to follow us on INSTAGRAM! http://www.instagram.com/brooklynandbailey

We told all of our friends that we needed them to help us film a video all about making friends in #college, but little did they know...we were about to trick them! We set the whole thing up to look like they were just going to be filming a video with me (Brooklyn), because Bailey was “at a meeting”. 😂 

Bailey was hiding out in the bathroom as I started the video, and a couple of minutes in, I went back to the bathroom and we SWITCHED PLACES! We went all out too, I even gave her all of my jewelry AND she wore hair extensions to look as much like me as possible… It was kind of scary how much she looked like me!! 😂 what do you think???

We even asked Asa (Bailey’s #boyfriend) to be a part of it, and y’all will never believe what happened during the video with him… 🙈We were so laughing SO HARD!!

You can’t help but feel so bad for him… but don’t blame Asa for not noticing, he got Bailey back a few days later and she didn’t notice he switched with one of our friends who looks a lot like him, during a photo shoot! What can they say??? They’ve been dating long distance for over 2 years and don’t spend a lot of time physically together!

Who were you the MOST surprised by that didn’t notice we switched places? Could you tell??? Comment below!

💋's - Brooklyn

snippet.title: The PAUSE Challenge! | TWIN vs TWIN
snippet.description:
Today, you'll watch us go head-to-head in the #PauseChallenge! Brooklyn and I are both VERY competitive, so we were each really determined to WIN this challenge! Who do you think will win??  🙈

✅ Don't forget to check out our new Brooklyn & Bailey mascara and hair / jewelry accessories!
https://brooklynandbaileyshop.com

Basically, this is a challenge is a current trend on YouTube (made famous by Brent Rivera, Sofie Dossi, Woody & Kleiny, Morgz, the Labrant Fam, Jake Paul, Sis vs Bro, etc) where you carry a remote around and "PAUSE" each other in any given scenario. That paused person has no choice but to FREEZE and funny things can happen! Of course, being competitive identical #twins, we ended up trying to get even with each other on every subsequent pause!

Oddly enough, there was a lot of water involved for us… 😂 I paused Brooklyn as she JUST stepped out of the shower, she spilled water all over my face as I was attempting to take a drink, and I even got her GOOD with the water hose as she just stood there! I mean, it’s hot in Texas, so I feel like maybe she should be thanking me for cooling her off? What do y'all think? 😂

I think the WORST moment to get paused is when you REALLY have to go to the bathroom! Brooklyn paused me just as I was getting up to go to the restroom, and I seriously thought I was going to burst! I just had to stand there and deal with "the pressure" because I’m not a quitter! (I, of course, got her back though... don’t you worry!)

I feel like the only question now is... who do YOU think won this Pause Challenge?? Brooklyn or Bailey? Comment below! 

This video was just as fun to film as our recent Twin Swap videos. You can check those out here!

👯‍♂️ Identical Twins Switch Places | Will Bailey’s Boyfriend Notice? (over 12 MILLION views)
https://youtu.be/Nun_4w8m_SY 

👯‍♂️ Identical Twins DRIVE THRU Swap Challenge (over 9 MILLION views)
https://youtu.be/HoLipntmsUE 

👯‍♂️ Identical Twins 2-Car DRIVE THRU Challenge (over 6 MILLION views)
https://youtu.be/P-SEulc_5vE 

👯‍♂️ Identical Twins PREGNANT with TWINS for 24 Hours! *not real* (over 2 MILLION views)
https://youtu.be/fqLAWwGOjxI

👯‍♂️ Identical Twin Wears a WIG in Public to See if Her Twin Sister Notices! (over 2 MILLION views)
https://youtu.be/H78hubx5Mwo

So, what do y'all think? Would you like to see a Part 2? What other TWIN videos would you like to see us film in the future? Comment below!

💋's - Bailey

snippet.title: Will Friends Tell Me that I SMELL BAD? Will Boyfriend Say Something? | True Friends Test
snippet.description:
Today we’ll see which of our friends are #TrueFriends by putting them to the test! Only a true friend feels comfortable telling you if you’re makeup looks BAD, or if you smell like a trash can… 🙊 Which of our friends will actually say something, and which ones won’t?? Watch until the end…

✅ Our sister Kamri just launched new STICKERS for your laptop, hydroflask, school supplies, and MORE! We love them, so check them out HERE: https://kamrinoel.com/collections/stickers 

As you guys know, we love playing pranks on our #friends and testing them when they’re completely unaware of what’s happening… 😎 In today’s video, we‘ll be doing different, funny things like doing our makeup badly, intentionally having something stuck in our teeth, and even smelling really badly to see which of our friends will tell actually tell us that something is off! 

It was difficult to take on this video, because it’s SO HARD to not just burst out laughing while playing out these scenarios! As we put Asa (Bailey’s #boyfriend) to test to see if he would call out Bailey’s bad makeup, we were dying laughing! Not only did he not notice how bad it was, he LIKED it! It really boils down to Asa just being such a nice guy and always thinking that Bailey looks good! 😂

snippet.title: $15,000 for My Bad Art on eBay?? | Twin VS Twin Challenge #WithMe
snippet.description:
Today we’re going to see if it’s possible to sell our #bad #art on #eBay! We came across a TikTok recently where a guy posted a pretty bad piece of art on eBay, but due to his strategy and how he described it, it sold for THOUSANDS of dollars! Do you think we will get any bids?? 🎨

✅ Check out all of our NEW APPAREL, mascara, jewelry, hair accessories, and MORE! https://brooklynandbaileyshop.com/

Of course, we had to turn this into a competition between the two of us, our younger sister @KamriNoel, and Bailey’s boyfriend, Asa! We each created our own paintings and came up with different strategies on how we should market them on eBay! 

All of our paintings ended up getting some SERIOUSLY high bids! Mine (Brooklyn) actually ended up getting the highest bid, and it was $15,100.00! Asa came in second place with a bid for $13,200.00, Kamri came in third place with a bid of $12,100.00, and last was Bailey’s bid for $10,800.00!

Going into the competition, we didn’t know if we would even get any bids at all. We agreed from the start though that if we did get any, we would be donating most of the money to a good cause. In the end, the bidders ended up not paying - so none of us made any money on our paintings this time! It was still incredibly fun to do though, and it was honestly a really cool experiment! 

✅Don’t forget to follow us on TikTok to see the video that we made! https://www.tiktok.com/@brooklynandbailey?lang=en

snippet.title: Dressing as CELEBRiTiES on College Campus | Ariana Grande, Billie Eilish, Taylor Swift & MORE!
snippet.description:
Today, y'all will watch us dress up as #celebrities ALL WEEK on campus! Yes, we even attended classes at our university wearing these outfits! How do you think we did??? (Special thanks to TheRealReal for partnering with us on this fun video!)

👉🏻 Click HERE for $25 OFF your first order from TheRealReal: http://bit.ly/2NqbM5w 

We’ve wanted to do a fun #challenge video like this for awhile now, after being such fans of Niki & Gabi over the years! We think it’s awesome to watch when they dress up as celebs in public, so we wanted to see if we could pull it off as well as they do! You can watch their amazing videos here: http://www.youtube.com/nikiandgabi

For this challenge, we dressed up as Taylor Swift, Miley Cyrus, Kylie Jenner, Ariana Grande, Billie Eilish, and Millie Bobby Brown while on Baylor's #College campus! These outfits were seriously so fun to dress up in! I think because the looks are so extreme, it really forced us outside of our comfort zone! Thanks to TheRealReal, we were able to find some really fun items to wear, to help us complete the looks! We found super cool thigh-high boots that we wore for both Miley Cyrus and Ariana Grande! We even found a super cool Gucci belt that paired up super well with the Miley Cyrus look. I think this video was even more fun for us because we generally don’t get wear many designer brands (due to expense), but TheRealReal made them so much more affordable! We purposefully chose to dress up as celebrities who have very unique styles, so that people around us would recognize who we were! We definitely had a lot of looks and double-takes as we walked around!
